sparql: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT ?producer (COUNT(?film) AS ?count) WHERE { ?film rdf:type dbo:Film . ?film dbo:producer ?producer . }

en_ques: how many employees does google have?
sparql: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT (COUNT(?employee) AS ?count) WHERE { dbr:Google dbo:employee ?employee . }

en_ques: give me all actors who were born in berlin.

en_ques: who created goofy?

en_ques: which music albums contain the song last christmas?

en_ques: in which city was the former dutch queen juliana buried?

en_ques: list all the musicals with music by leonard bernstein.

en_ques: give me all companies in the advertising industry.
sparql: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?company WHERE { ?company rdf:type dbo:Company . ?company dbo:industry ?industry . FILTER (REGEX(?industry, "advertising", "i")) }

en_ques: what is the largest metropolitan area in washington state?
sparql: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> SELECT ?item WHERE { ?item dbo:type dbr:Metropolitan_area . ?item dbp:subdivisionName dbr:Washington_(state) . ?item dbo:populationTotal ?population . }

en_ques: who killed john lennon?
sparql: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT ?x WHERE { res:John_Lennon dbo:deathCause ?x . }

en_ques: which writers studied in istanbul?
sparql: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?writer WHERE { ?writer a dbo:Writer . ?writer dbo:education ?education . ?education dbo:city dbr:Istanbul . }
